## Element Theory

The Color theory gives rise to the Element theory. Because the Matter/Antimatter combination can be described by a cube it can be seen that a single paired Matter/Antimatter combination has five possible options. The Element theory then has 5 possible Elements: Earth, Metal, Water, Wood, and Fire. 
